title: BigFish - Mystery P.I.  The Vegas Heist - Hidden Object - Reques
description:
Mystery P.I.: The Vegas Heist

Mystery P.I. - The Vegas Heist takes you to the 
glitz and glamour of Las Vegas where the heist of 
the century has just occurred. Over $4 Billion in 
cash has been stolen from the state`s newest casino 
the day before its grand opening. The casino has 
hired you to find & return the money before the 
doors open the next day. Hurry - you only have 
16 hours to return the money back to the casino!

    * Investigate Vegas
    * Great art and story
    * Unique mini-games
    * Don&#039;t forget the original mystery: The Lottery Ticket
System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP/Vista
CPU: 600 Mhz
RAM: 256 MB
DirectX: 7.0
Hard Drive: 42 MB
